<li>Ratzinger, Joseph Cardinal (Benedict XVI) (9 October 2002). "St. Josemaria: God is very much at work in our world today". <i>L'Osservatore Romano Weekly Edition in English</i>, p. 3. — online <a href="http://www.ewtn.com/library/curia/cdfjosma.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.ewtn.com/library/curia/cdfjosma.htm" rel="nofollow">here</a></li>
